\c 6
\s Modhekai anokudzwa
\p
\v 1 Zvino usiku uhwo mambo akashaiwa hope, akaraira kuti vauye nebhuku yamashoko aMakoronike, akaravirwa mambo.
\v 2 Vakawana kuti pakanyorwa kuti Modhekai akadeya kuzivisa mashoko aBhigitana naTereshi, varanda vaviri vamambo pakati pavarindi vomukova, vakatsvaka kuuraya mambo Ahashivheroshi.
\v 3 Ipapo mambo akati, Modhekai akakudzwa nokurumbidzwa sei pamusoro pechinhu ichi? Varanda vamambo vaimubatira vakati, Haana chaakaitirwa.
\p
\v 4 Mambo akati, Ndianiko uri paruvanze? Zvino Hamani akange apinda paruvanze rwokunze kweimba yamambo, achida kukumbira kuna mambo kuti Modhekai asungirirwe namatanda aakange amugadzirira.
\v 5 Varanda vamambo vakati kwaari, Tarirai Hamani umire paruvanze. Mambo akati, Ngaapinde.
\p
\v 6 Naizvozvo Hamani akapinda. Mambo akati kwaari, Munhu, mambo waanoda kumukudza, angaitirweiko? Zvino Hamani akati mumoyo make, Mambo vangada kukudza aniko, asi ini?
\p
\v 7 Hamani akati kuna mambo, Iye munhu, mambo waanoda kukudza,
\v 8 ngaatorerwe nguwo dzoushe, idzo dzinosifukwa namambo, nebhiza rinositasva namambo, nekorona youshe inosidzikwa pamusoro wake;
\v 9 zvino nguwo nebhiza ngazviiswe pamaoko omumwe wamachinda amambo anokudzwa kwazvo, kuti vafukidze munhu uyo, mambo waanoda kukudza, vagomufambisa munzira dzomuguta, akatasva bhiza, vadanidzire pamberi pake, vachiti, Munhu, mambo waanoda kukudza, ngaaitirwe saizvozvo.
\p
\v 10 Ipapo mambo akati kuna Hamani, Chimbidzika utore nguwo nebhiza, sezvawataura, undoitira Modhekai muJudha saizvozvo, iye agere pasuwo ramambo; usarega shoko rimwe pamashoko ose awataura.
\p
\v 11 Zvino Hamani akatora nguwo nebhiza, akafukidza Modhekai, akamufambisa panzira dzomuguta akatasva bhiza, akadanidzira pamberi pake, achiti, Ndizvo zvichaitirwa munhu uyo mambo waanoda kukudza.
\p
\v 12 Zvino Modhekai akadzokera kusuwo ramambo. Asi Hamani akachimbidzika kuenda kumba kwake achichema, akafukidza musoro wake.
\v 13 Hamani akarondedzera kuna Zereshi mukadzi wake neshamwari dzake dzose zvose zvaakaitirwa. Ipapo shamwari dzake dzakangwara naZereshi mukadzi wake vakati kwaari, Kana Modhekai uyu wawakatanga kuwa pamberi pake ari worudzi rwavaJudha, haungakundi, asi zvirokwazvo uchawa pamberi pake.
\v 14 Vakati vachataura naye, varanda vamambo vakasvika, vakachimbidzika kuenda naHamani kumafundo akange agadzirwa naEsiteri.
